0height%3D%5C%222075%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmily%20Sundberg%20started%20her%20Feed%20Me%20Substack%20as%20a%20side%20project%20when%20she%20was%20working%20at%20Meta.%20Now%20it's%20a%20thriving%2C%20one-person%20business.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Sundberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEmily%20Sundberg%20used%20to%20work%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20helping%20to%20sell%20Instagram%20ads.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20she%20sells%20ads%20for%20herself%2C%20on%20her%20very%20buzzy%20Feed%20Me%20newsletter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe's%20part%20of%20a%20new%20crop%20of%20Substack%20authors%20running%20one-person%20media%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20increasingly%20high-profile%20one.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20lots%20of%20Emily%20Sundbergs%20in%20New%20York%20City%20%E2%80%94%20striving%20young%20people%20who%20show%20up%20intent%20on%20making%20a%20name%20for%20themselves%20in%20media%2C%20finance%2C%20or%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20only%20one%20actual%20Emily%20Sundberg%2C%20who%20has%20turned%20that%20ethos%20into%20a%20one-person%20media%20company%3A%20Her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.readfeedme.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFeed%20Me%3C%2Fa%3E%20newsletter%20has%20become%20an%20increasingly%20popular%20read%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20know%20what%20people%20with%20money%20and%20ambition%20are%20spending%20their%20money%20on%20%E2%80%94%20and%20who%20also%20want%20to%20know%20about%20the%20businesses%20that%20cater%20to%20those%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESundberg%20started%20her%20Substack%20when%20she%20had%20a%20full-time%20job%20in%20business%20marketing%20at%20Meta%20%E2%80%94%20which%20she%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bbasically%20being%2C%20'You're%20a%20small%20business%20in%20Miami.%20You%20should%20use%20Instagram%20ads.'%26quot%3B%20Then%20she%