%20that%20I%20was%20working%20for%20weren't%20green-lighting%20my%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20lesson%20in%20trusting%20myself%2C%20and%20my%20gut%20and%20intuition%2C%20and%20making%20something%20in%20a%20white%20space%20that%20didn't%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20was%20like%3A%20%26quot%3BOK%2C%20I'm%20onto%20something.%20I'm%20trusting%20myself.%20I'm%20gonna%20lean%20into%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20you%20think%20about%20making%20yourself%20the%20face%2Fbrand%2Fmain%20character%20of%20your%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20newsletter%2C%20I%20did%20have%20a%20selfie%20on%20it%20every%20day.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20if%20selfies%20were%20popular%20on%20LinkedIn%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20I%20do%20think%20that%20I%20got%20an%20initial%20bump%20in%20traffic.%20Because%20people%20were%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BShe's%20talking%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Femilysundberg_credit-agreement-day-at-feed-me-activity-7138199398835998720-xMTV%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20credit%20restructuring%20of%20Rent%20the%20Runway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20she's%20a%20young%20woman%2C%20and%20there's%20anime%20hearts%20around%20this%20selfie%20of%20her.%20What%20is%20going%20on%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20helped%20at%20the%20beginning.%20And%20then%2C%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20I%20did%20a%20proper%20branding%20of%20the%20letter.%20The%20selfies%20went%20away.%20I%20had%20too%20many%20weird%20interactions%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%20can%20be%20a%20double-edged%20sword%2C%20right%3F%20You've%20attained%20some%20sort%20of%20status%2Fcelebrity%20notoriety.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20you%20have%20creeps%20coming%20up%20in%20the%20street.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20really%20happy%20that%20I%20stopped%20doing%20the%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20funny%20%E2%80%94%20as%20I'm%20doing%20the%20ad%20sales