%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Shark%20Turboblade%20Fan%20in%20vertical%20mode%20with%20swivelled%20vents.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685efa7ff748d8c055f49342%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20love%20using%20the%20horizontal%20mode%20as%20I%20sleep%2C%20and%20the%20vertical%20tower%20mode%20is%20excellent%20for%20focused%20cooling.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Turboblade%20has%20an%20incredibly%20versatile%20and%20interesting%20design.%20Its%20main%20selling%20point%20is%20its%20swivel%20head%20with%20adjustable%20vents.%20The%20head%2C%20which%20sits%20on%20an%20adjustable%20base%2C%20can%20be%20moved%20from%20a%20vertical%20tower%20position%20to%20a%20horizontal%20position%20for%20widespread%20air%20circulation.%20The%20vents%20also%20swivel%2C%20so%20you%20can%20send%20air%20flowing%20in%20different%20directions%20to%20get%20the%20perfect%20amount%20of%20cooling.%20It%20also%20oscillates%20180%20degrees%20to%20provide%20steady%20and%20smooth%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fan%20has%20controls%20on%20the%20base%20and%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20remote%2C%20which%20conveniently%20clicks%20into%20place%20with%20a%20magnet%20behind%20the%20fan's%20head.%20With%20the%20remote%2C%20you%20can%20also%20turn%20on%20oscillation%2C%20set%20a%20timer%20for%20up%20to%2012%20hours%2C%20and%20change%20the%20fan's%20horizontal%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Turboblade%20also%20has%20a%20panel%20that%20blocks%20dust%20from%20getting%20into%20your%20fan.%20To%20clean%20it%2C%20just%20pop%20the%20panel%20off%20and%20clear%20away%20any%20dust.%20It's%20completely%20bladeless%2C%20so%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20dusting%20the%20blades%20or%20small%20fingers%20trying%20to%20get%20into%20grates.%20It%20comes%20in%20two%20colors%2C%20white%20and%20charcoal%2C%20both%20of%20which%20look%20modern%20with%20gold%20detailing.%20Aesthetically%2C%20it's%20a%20beautiful%20fan%20that%20blends%20seamlessly%20in%20any%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2212e8d77d-c346-4e9f-b548-1fa2471401fe%5C%22%3ECycle%20between%2010%20speeds%20and%203%20special%20modes%20to%20find%20your%20favorite%20setting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Turboblade%20pieces%20laid%20in%20a%20row%2C%20clearly%20marked%20with%20bright%20yellow%20stickers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685efb523d5881a51c1c4bc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shark%20Turboblade%20is%20so%20easy%20to%20assemble%2C%20even%20I%20couldn't%20mess%20it%20up.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20finally%20received%20my%20coveted%20fan%2C%20it%20took%20less%20than%20five%20minutes%20to%20unbox%20and%20set%20up.%20I%20connected%20a%20blade%20to%20the%20head%20and%20the%20swivel%20to%20the%20base%2C%20and%20it's%20ready%20to%20go.%20The%20fan%20turned%20on%20with%20a%20chime%20as%20I%20explored%20the%20modes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fan%20has%2010%20speeds%2C%20all%20of%20which%20have%20a%20traditional%20soothing%20fan%20sound%2C%20despite%20not%20having%20blades.%20There%20are%20also%20three%20special%20modes%3A%20natural%20breeze%2C%20sleep%2C%20and%20breeze%20boost.%20Sleep%20mode%20turns%20off%20chimes%20and%20lights%2C%20while%20breeze%20boost%20has%20a%20powerful%20burst%20of%20air.%20The%20natural%20breeze%20mode%20cycles%20through%20fan%20speeds%20to%20mimic%20natural%20wind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holding%20a%20remote%20above%20the%20Shark%20Turboblade%20Fan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685efae5f748d8c055f49355%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20remote%20attaches%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20fan%20with%20a%20magnet%2C%20so%20I%20never%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20losing%20it.%20TV%20remotes%2C%20take%20note.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20sleep%20hot%2C%20I%20usually%20keep%20the%20fan%20on%20high%20speed%3A%20around%206%20or%207.%20It's%20still%20noticeably%20cool%20on%20low%20settings%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20the%20feel%20and%20sound%20of%20a%20high%20speed.%20I%20like%20a%20fan%20for%20white%20noise%20as%20a%20sleep%2C%20but%20the%20low%20settings%20are%20much%20quieter%20if%20you%20prefer%20complete%20silence%2C%20too.%20When%20testing%20decibels%2C%20the%20lowest%20setting%20was%20barely%20noticeable%2C%20while%20the%20highest%20setting%20was%20about%2060%20decibels%2C%20which%20is%20comparable%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20a%20running%20dishwasher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20travels%20across%20the%20room.%20I%20can%20feel%20the%20air%20all%20throughout%20my%20bedroom%20when%20the%20fan%20is%20on.%20I%20also%20placed%20it%20on%20one%20end%20of%20my%20hallway%20and%20stood%20at%20the%20opposite%20end%2C%20and%20I%20could%20still%20feel%20the%20cool%20breeze.%20It's%20small%20but%20mighty%2C%20with%20powerful%20cooling%20that%20traverses%20the%20entire%20house.%20Both%20low%20and%20high%20settings%20performed%20well%20when%20tested%20with%20a%20windometer%20at%201.7%20meters%20per%20second%20and%20five%20meters%20per%20second%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22265f579b-5253-40d9-a1ac-326cfb333c25%5C%22%3EThe%20Air%20Blanket%20mode%20is%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20sleeping%20cool%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Shark%20Turboblade%20Fan%20pointed%20at%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20green%20duvet%20cover.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685efbd785e81483682cfac1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20keep%20the%20fan%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20my%20bed%20every%20night%20so%20I%20can%20use%20the%20Air%20Blanket%20mode%2C%20which%20covers%20the%20top%20of%20my%20bed%20in%20a%20soothing%20sheet%20of%20cool%20air.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20really%20sold%20me%20on%20this%20fan%20was%20the%20Air%20Blanket%20mode%2C%20which%20promises%20to%20keep%20you%20cool%20as%20you%20sleep.%20After%20playing%20around%20with%20the%20fan's%20settings%2C%20I%20discovered%20that%20the%20Air%20Blanket%20isn't%20actually%20a%20mode%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20just%20describes%20the%20horizontal%20positioning%20of%20the%20fan%20when%20placed%20at%20bed%20height.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20vents%20pointed%20forwards%2C%20a%20sheet%20of%20air%20runs%20over%20you.%20I%20use%20this%20orientation%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20my%20bed%20at%20night%2C%20and%20it's%20like%20a%20burst%20of%20air%20is%20my%20very%20own%20blanket%20atop%20my%20comforter.%20It%20blows%20on%20my%20face%20all%20night%2C%20which%20prevents%20overheating.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20wide%20enough%20to%20keep%20me%20and%20my%20partner%20cool%20in%20our%20king-size%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Turboblade's%20shape%20and%20bladeless%20design%20make%20the%20Air%20Blanket%20mode%20truly%20unique.%20Unlike%20a%20typical%20tower%20or%20box%20fan%2C%20which%20relies%20on%20oscillation%20to%20keep%20multiple%20people%20in%20bed%20cool%2C%20the%20Turboblade%20has%20consistent%2C%20reliable%20cooling%20across%20the%20entire%20bed.%20It's%20a%20rival%20to%20expensive%20bed%20cooling%20systems%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Feight-sleep-pod-4-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEight%20Sleep%20Pod%204%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20cools%20the%20bed's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ab0b19e-5760-4a8e-8608-a0dc3bd2d1eb%5C%22%3EIt's%20portable%20to%20use%20in%20every%20room%20of%20my%20house%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Shark%20Turboblade%20Fan%20horizontal%20with%20green%20curtains%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ef9fdf748d8c055f49311%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20rotate%20each%20fan%20to%20the%20direction%20of%20your%20choosing%20to%20direct%20airflow.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20using%20the%20Turboblade%20beyond%20my%20bedroom%2C%20too.%20At%20just%20under%2015%20pounds%20with%20a%20compact%20design%2C%20the%20fan%20is%20easily%20portable.%20I%20carry%20the%20fan%20by%20the%20base%20to%20move%20it%20around%20the%20house.%20Plus%2C%20the%20swivel%20vents%20let%20you%20put%20the%20fan%20in%20any%20position%2C%20so%20you%20can%20different%20directions%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20horizontal%20mode%20is%20great%20for%20wide%20coverage%2C%20whereas%20the%20tower%20mode%20is%20best%20for%20focused%20cooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brought%20it%20into%20my%20living%20room%20on%20one%20particularly%20humid%20Saturday%2C%20put%20it%20in%20tower%20mode%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20my%20day%20sweat-free.%20I'd%20normally%20reach%20for%20the%20thermostat%20when%20I%20feel%20myself%20overheating%2C%20but%20I've%20now%20started%20opting%20for%20my%20fan%20instead.%20I'm%20hoping%20that%20this%20will%20help%20save%20my%20electricity%20bill%2C%20especially%20as%20we%20start%20to%20move%20into%20summer.%20I%20used%20an%20energy%20tracking%20plug%20and%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20see%20that%20the%20fan%20only%20used%20about%2050%20watts%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20total%20cost%20to%20run%20the%20fan%20for%2024%20hours%20is%20%240.19.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272d99611-138f-43df-bcc4-b86c6da985f4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Turboblade%20has%20few%20cons.%20At%20%242