3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20our%20server%20arrives%2C%20I%20order%20the%20onion%20soup%20and%20New%20York%20strip%20steak.%20We%20treat%20ourselves%20to%20Diet%20Cokes.%20They%20come%20with%20a%20lemon%20and%20make%20me%20feel%20very%20elegant.%20(If%20you%20prefer%20your%20business%20lunches%20boozy%2C%20there%20are%20ample%20options.)%20My%20boss%20goes%20with%20shrimp%2C%20and%20my%20friend%2C%20feeling%20%3Cem%3Every%3C%2Fem%3E%20elegant%2C%20opts%20for%20filet%20mignon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20server%20brings%20our%20drinks%2C%20soups%2C%20and%20vegetable%20rice.%20Cooking%20the%20fried%20rice%20is%20usually%20a%20star%20of%20the%20show%20during%20regular%20Benihana%20meals%2C%20but%20the%2045-minute%20pledge%20demands%20some%20sacrifices%20%E2%80%94%20bearing%20witness%20to%20the%20dark%20arts%20of%20egg-scrambling%2C%20I'm%20not.%20The%20rice%20comes%20pre-portioned%20in%20small%20white%20bowls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22soups%2C%20rices%2C%20diet%20cokes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ef9553d5881a51c1c4b1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20vegetable%20rice%2C%20soups%2C%20and%20Diet%20Cokes.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Kleeman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rice%20is%20hot%20and%20peppery%2C%20and%20I%20could%20eat%20seven%20bowls%20of%20it.%20The%20soup%2C%20a%20dark%20brown%20broth%20with%20spring%20onions%20and%20mushrooms%20bobbing%20around%2C%20is%20salty%20and%20delicious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20minute%20eight%2C%20our%20chef%20wheels%20a%20cart%20over%20and%20starts%20preparing%20the%20grill.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20oiling%20and%20clanging%20and%20tossing%20of%20kitchen%20utensils%20in%20the%20air.%20If%20I%20was%20this%20chef%2C%20I%20would%20be%20overcome%20with%20stage%20fright%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20reason%20I%20am%20not%20this%20chef.%3C%2Fp%3E