to%20us%20but%20delightful%20nonetheless%2C%20our%20chef%20plopped%20some%20pieces%20of%20steak%20in%20the%20mustard%20sauce.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Kleeman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20strong%20woman%20isn't%20afraid%20to%20admit%20when%20she's%20wrong.%20When%20we%20dig%20in%2C%20everything%20is%20hot%2C%20chargrilled%2C%20and%20well%20seasoned.%20The%20veggies%20are%20nice%20and%20crispy.%20The%20steak%20is%20a%20hair%20overdone%20%E2%80%94%20somewhere%20around%20medium%20%E2%80%94%20but%20for%20less%20than%20twenty%20bucks%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20complain%20too%20much.%20The%20portions%20are%20generous%3A%20My%20boss%20receives%2011%20shrimp%2C%20and%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20both%20get%20healthy-sized%20cuts%20of%20steak.%20After%20I%20sample%20the%20other%20dishes%2C%20I%20secretly%20decide%20that%20I%20chose%20the%20best%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20minute%2017%2C%20after%20he%20delivers%20our%20food%2C%20our%20chef%20bids%20us%20farewell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20eat%2C%20I%20ask%20my%20companions%20for%20their%20takes%20so%20far.%20My%20boss%20says%20that%20his%20shrimp%20is%20%26quot%3Bdelightfully%20cooked%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20vibes%20are%20%26quot%3Bawesome.%26quot%3B%20My%20reporter%20friend%20says%20that%20she%20loves%20the%20%26quot%3Bcelebratory%20air.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20reason%20I%20wouldn't%20come%20every%20day%20is%20because%20I%20would%20want%20it%20to%20feel%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20it's%20very%20heavy.%26quot%3B%20I%20agree%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20later%20that%20night%2C%20I%20would%20go%20on%20to%20eat%20a%20big%20bowl%20of%20pasta%20and%20three%20large%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies%20while%20watching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftom-cruise-own-stunts-real-mission-impossible-scientology-career-relevant-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETom%20Cruise%20almost%20die%20crawli