aption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPratibha%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20starting%20Pearl%20Mithila%20Makhana%20involved%20experiences%20of%20wading%20into%20muddy%20waters%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20documenting%20the%20laborious%20process%20of%20collecting%20the%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseeds%2C%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAugust%20to%20November%20is%20a%20busy%20time%20for%20him%2C%20as%20this%20is%20the%20period%20when%20the%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseeds%20are%20harvested.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20year%2C%20farmers%20would%20see%20a%20lull%20in%20activity.%20But%20not%20anymore.%20Pratibha%E2%80%99s%20brand%20keeps%20them%20busy.%20Farming%20families%2C%20especially%20the%20women%2C%20are%20engaged%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Epost-harvesting%20that%20unfolds%20at%20the%20factory%20outlet%2C%20where%20the%20seeds%20are%20sun-dried%20to%20render%20them%20a%20longevity%20to%20survive%20transport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seeds%20are%20graded%20using%20a%20sieve%20to%20separate%20them%20according%20to%20sizes.%20Then%20follows%20tempering%20to%20loosen%20the%20kernel%20within%20and%20have%20it%20pop%20out%20of%20the%20black%20coloured%20seed.%20The%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20is%20then%20once%20again%20cleaned%20and%20hand-sorted%20%3C%2Fem%3Einto%20sizes%20and%20makes%20its%20way%20to%20you.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288654%2Fhealth-benefits-of-superfood-makhana-fox-nuts-helps-in-weight-loss%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebestseller%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Erasgulla%20makhana%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20measures%20around%2022%20mm%2C%20Pratibha%20notes%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20is%20a%20favourite%20of%20mothers%20who%20have%20young%20children.%20But%2C%20she%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20also%20the%20most%20difficult%20one%20to%20procure.%20In%20a%20100%20kg%20batch